- Ella: 85% for 3-5 days
- Plan B: 88% within 72 hours, decreases to 58% by 96 hours
- Copper IUD: 99.9%
- Yuzpe: 75% (not commonly used now)

- Eligibility:
- All women can use some form of EC
- No routine screening needed
- Advance prescription available in some states

- Counseling:
- Use as soon as possible after unprotected sex
- Regular contraception needed afterward
- No protection for STIs
- Can be used multiple times
- Does not cause abortion

**Counseling Framework:**
- GATHER (Greet, Ask, Tell, Explain, Return)
- Reproductive life plan discussion
- Shared decision making
- Respect patient preferences
- Cultural sensitivity
- Trauma-informed care
